    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
