    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a reliable source of parts? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for an enthusiast who loves a hands-on challenge. Grab this opportunity to own a classic model at a budget-friendly price!",
